apt-get install cmake
apt-get install libsdl2-2.0-0 libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev
apt-get install libgl1-mesa-dev
apt-get install libglew-dev libglm-dev 
apt-get install libfreetype6 libfreetype6-dev
apt-get install libassimp4 libassimp-dev assimp-utils

Building using premake, due to unsupported feature in cmake for precompiled headers (cmake files are still included in tmp folder if you want)

***Unix***:
./premake/premake5 gmake 
make

***Windows***:
./premake/premake5.exe vs2015/17/19

Check premake-wiki for more information
url: https://github.com/premake/premake-core/wiki/


